@Pete Krautscheid VRDR BaseMessage parser is throwing error when I try to parse the TRX file. Ack messages pass without any issues.
"Parser: The property 'code' has an empty string value, which is not allowed. (at line 1, 1402)" NH21001_TRX_000001.JSON
Hi @Sirisha Sathyamurthy, thanks for including the file, we'll take a look
Hi @Sirisha Sathyamurthy, it does look like the file that was returned has an empty string for a code, which isn't allowed. I'll work with @Veronique at NCHS to figure out what's going on.
